column5: What the heck does that mean?

It means that the thread has deteriorated into a mud slinging match or something undesireable, and as a result the moderators have closed the discussion. It is in the rules that you agreed to when you joined the forum.
Theres rules here,Hell.Wheres my beer.  Sry Wayne.
You must be new, sometimes they want to prevent confrontation.
To me its when the thread becomes uninformative and pointless.
Then most threads would be under lock and key......
Shucks you beat me to it
